-- DCIM test data for local development (Physical/inventory + Logical designs).
-- Mirrors the retired dcim-frontend mocks at prototype scale so every
-- mock->API conversion can be exercised end to end.
--
-- ID convention: 019dc<TT>0-0000-7000-8000-0000000000NN, where <TT> identifies
-- the table (10=site, 20=room, 30=row, 40=rack, 50=catalog, 6x=port def,
-- 70=port compat, 80=asset, 90=asset event, a0=placement, b0=physical conn,
-- c0=note, d0=design, d1=logical device, d2=logical conn, d3=layout).

